{"tid":2420090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[飯民散水推特赦警暴攻略]顏純鈎:不能被運動中的部份激進派綁架","createTime":"2021-02-23T16:27:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T08:10:42.000Z","uid":26770,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b47aa367b3f99a1e79580e1bdaf84b73e352aec3","tid":2420090,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T16:27:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2419874/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2419874/page/1</a><br />\n簡單講就係顏純鈎提議飯民所有政黨合併由飯民大元首指揮<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"x-large\">飯民大元首實際就係飯民元老會,支持特赦警魔輪姦的何俊仁就是飯民8老其中一個</span></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2417343/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2417343/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n呢段最緊要<br />\n<br />\n'不能被運動中的部份激進派綁架，一說到大台就大驚失色，一說到領導就有犯罪感。那些拒絕大台的人，就讓他們拒絕好了，'<br />\n<br />\n<ins>姐係係唔加入大台做手下就係鬼<br />\n郁本土台,郁時事台就係第一步,因為呢班人有一定影響力又唔受操縱,<br />\n當你支持35+時咪笑笑口叫你手足, 你批評飯民咪變支足</ins>"},{"pid":"bd6e644c6bed59330bdc1fccc09517c707f692f5","tid":2420090,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T16:33:38.000Z","msg":"<strong>要推特赦警暴最大阻礙就係來自反政府群眾</strong><br />\n所以一定要先起大台同搵KOL抹黑不受飯民操縱的平台<br />\n<br />\n飯民唔係靜左, 班人一步步攪緊野<br />\n<br />\n點解何俊仁唔公開認錯再宣佈問責退黨<br />\n點解去到提議特赦強姦無KOL出聲<br />\n點解燒山親自見公民黨/民主黨,但兩黨死都唔成立警暴資料庫方便追究<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>因為一追究成萬罪犯就社會不穩,所以有人想提出特赦警暴</strong>"},{"pid":"a671af069537b08366c1294fb50a259e3956acdb","tid":2420090,"uid":88134,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T16:43:00.000Z","msg":"販民正式通過社運法<br />\n入面有兩大罪名<br />\n1. 煽動顛覆販民大台罪<br />\n2. 危害龍門安全罪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714443b20741e93ec34e5e7d14999bc197c2db61","tid":2420090,"uid":60527,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T16:44:13.000Z","msg":"班廢物真係陰魂不散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6521a3b371841429277288c70e34b7d2fa005644","tid":2420090,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T16:45:58.000Z","msg":"唔服從大台指揮就係社會少數極端份子<br />\n所以邊個攪大台就屌邊個<br />\n<br />\n呢班人個名太臭, 次次攪大台都騎劫散水"},{"pid":"c535737b54e216ab8caf1ecee8b641e0651029a8","tid":2420090,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T16:49:04.000Z","msg":"飯民無勢力啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果係還番幾十年既人血饅頭還好"},{"pid":"41219d628a5ee6b191969a4a229eec9b5a0185f3","tid":2420090,"uid":107681,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T16:54:10.000Z","msg":"使鳩你特赦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n集中營既猶太人居然討論特赦納粹黨<br />\n<br />\n傾下點樣避開聽日入毒氣室好過<br />\n<br />\n分清莊閒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d7649442e540e761660704284675391df0317c3","tid":2420090,"uid":319935,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a671af069537b08366c1294fb50a259e3956acdb","tid":2420090,"uid":88134,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T16:43:00.000Z","msg":"販民正式通過社運法<br />\n入面有兩大罪名<br />\n1. 煽動顛覆販民大台罪<br />\n2. 危害龍門安全罪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T16:55:54.000Z","msg":"關龍門咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6006a2982169f3e730d6a0caa73b7f47c423acd","tid":2420090,"uid":26770,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"41219d628a5ee6b191969a4a22